videos.description: Syracuse's Andrew White III makes the 3-pointer before Duke's Jayson Tatum answers with a 3-pointer of his own in the tight ACC matchup.
videos.headline: Syracuse and Duke trade 3-pointers

videos.description: Jayson Tatum collects the rebound and goes coast to coast for the layup to extend Duke's lead over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Duke's Jayson Tatum continues strong start with layup

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard makes the corner 3-pointer after the foul isn't called on the other end for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Jim Boeheim can't believe no call, leads to Duke 3-pointer

videos.description: John Gillon makes the 3-pointer after getting free with the crossover to keep Syracuse close in the first half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Gillon sends Tatum to floor with crossover, nails 3-pointer

videos.description: John Gillon keeps Syracuse within striking distance against Duke with the athletic finish at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Gillon hangs in the air for scoop

videos.description: John Gillon makes the and-1 layup as Syracuse tries to close the gap against Duke.
videos.headline: Gillon continues to torch Duke's defense

videos.description: Syracuse forces the turnover on the Duke inbound play and John Gillon takes it himself for the layup.
videos.headline: Gillon explodes down the lane for layup

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard completes the 3-point play after faking out the defender at the foul line.
videos.headline: Kennard uses pump fake for and-1 layup

videos.description: Gillon's layup helps Syracuse keep things close at home against Duke.
videos.headline: Gillon brings fans to their feet with layup

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum throws down the alley-oop before John Gillon comes back with the 3-pointer for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Duke and Syracuse trading blows in the Carrier Dome

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum makes the extra pass to a wide open Luke Kennard for the 3-pointer against Syracuse.
videos.headline: Two man game between Tatum and Kennard leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke's Amile Jefferson completes the 3-point play after Luke Kennard finds him with the entry pass.
videos.headline: Duke's Jefferson finishes strong underneath

videos.description: Tyus Battle makes the long jumper for Syracuse in a close game against Duke.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle makes long jumper

videos.description: Tyler Lydon scores the easy bucket for Syracuse after the great up and under move.
videos.headline: Syracuse refuse to back down to Duke

videos.description: Jayson Tatum shows off his athleticism by catching the lob in stride for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Tatum rises for alley-oop

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon caps off monster night with the game-winning buzzer-beater against No. 10 Duke.
videos.headline: Syracuse takes down Duke as 3-pointer banks in at the buzzer

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon talks about being unstoppable on his game-winning shot against Duke.
videos.headline: Gillon keeps Syracuse's tournament hopes alive with buzzer beater

videos.description: Dick Vitale and Karl Ravech talk about the importance of Syracuse's late season win over Duke.
videos.headline: Breaking down Syracuse's dramatic win over Duke

videos.description: John Gillion sinks the dagger at the buzzer as part of a 26-point night, and Syracuse knocks off No. 10 Duke 78-75.
videos.headline: Gillion clutch, lifting Cuse past Duke at buzzer

videos.description: Jim Boeheim explains how important it was for Syracuse to beat Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Boeheim admits Cuse got lucky) 2017/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boeheim admits Cuse got lucky
